data.title: Daniel Strickland
data.content: Our Program Manager Donna represented Mission Australia at the Flag Raising Ceremony in Eden earlier today to lunch #naidocweek2018 National NAIDOC Thanks for the pics Donna and great to hear that Ozzie Cruse gave an explanation of the flags and a wonderful welcome by Ozzie’s son BJ Cruse. @mission_aust #naidoc2018 #naidocweek #naidoc #eden #begavalley #aboriginal #australia #closingthegap #missionaustralia #becauseofherwecan #newselfwales
